♪ 'Round the Cape Horn to Valpariso ♪

02:06:14.650 --> 02:06:22.350
♪ Red the port light,
starboard the green ♪

02:06:23.400 --> 02:06:30.550
♪ How will she know of the devils I've seen ♪

